question: Which restaurant is available towards Nokomis Naturescape Garden, Minneapolis, MN within 140 kilometers from Magnetic Originals, Minneapolis, MN?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.297652 44.948093)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.234364 44.913029)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.297652 44.948093)',4326)::geography, 140000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.297652 44.948093)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
